title: 3 and Out - Pro Bowl, Eagles/WFT & Rams/Hawks Recap, Week 16 Preview, Mailbag

John gives some outside the box Pro Bowl takes, reacts the Tuesday Eagles/WFT and Rams/Seahawks games, previews the top week 16 matchups, and answers listener questions in Middlekauff Mailbag.
